Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=34=110}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido e peça desculpas logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:05.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse cara quer morrer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:13.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que você tá começando a ver\No quanto foi imprudente!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:19.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É por isso que você tá com tanto medo que nem consegue falar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:20.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Há pouco,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:27.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,um homem com nariz comprido e uma mulher\Nde cabelo comprido cruzaram nosso caminho,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:30.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,então nosso capitão tá de mau humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Peça desculpas rápido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se prostre!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:39.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Caso contrário, esse pequeno erro\Nvai acabar custando sua vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:43.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nosso capitão tem o dedo fácil no gatilho.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:50.45,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ajoelha no chão de uma vez!\NEsse cara é o Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:53.27,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele {\i1}quer{\i0} morrer? Peça desculpas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preciso ir embora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.30,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,– Qual é o problema dele?!\N– Qual é o problema dele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:45.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:53.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, ele fez alguma coisa agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:02.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu queria ir pescar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode, cabeça de bagre!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:08.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que não?! E por que eu deveria te ouvir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:13.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você acha que eu tô andando\Ncom você porque eu quero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:17.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você vai me dar mais dor de cabeça\Nse sair vagando por aí de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sua bola de musgo confusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:23.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo vai chegar logo,\Nentão só me siga até o navio!
Comment: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:24.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que saco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é o sétimo pra ficar mandando\Nno primeiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:36.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você tá nos classificando\Npela ordem que a gente chegou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:40.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você ter sido o primeiro foi pura sorte,\Nentão não deixa subir à cabeça!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, foi mal... número sete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom, você pediu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu treinei minhas pernas no inferno por dois anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:54.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode vir! Eu te corto no meio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:02.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Senti falta de vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:14.80,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:16.97,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.07,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:25.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S... Sogeking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.11,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês mudaram nesses dois anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aposto que ficaram mais fortes!
Comment: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:34.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hmm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São os Chapéu de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que eles tão fazendo na rua?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, o que aconteceu foi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:45.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Evite contato visual.\NVocê não quer lutar com eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,D-Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com você?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Senti calafrios por todo o corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que tipo de truque ele usou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:04.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah é! Temos outro problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É que a Cocoa foi–
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, quer dizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Nico Robin foi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Nico Robin foi sequestrada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:16.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe. Aconteceu bem na nossa frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:19.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, isso mesmo! Isso é sério, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:22.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela pode ter sido raptada,\Nassim como a Camie foi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:23.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem fez isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã... Não faço a menor ideia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:37.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,acho que as pessoas que estão atrás\Nda Robin verdadeira levaram a Cocoa por engano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É possível.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:44.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela era tão parecida com a Robin verdadeira...\NIsso não jogou a nosso favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, parem de cochichar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, não tem muito o que fazer agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o destino dela.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,T-Tá bom, Capitão.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:56.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy! A Robin foi sequestrada!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E que diabo de criatura é essa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é algum tipo de piada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora não é hora de falar essas coisas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:13.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como ele fala? É um bicho de pelúcia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Retira o que disse, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esquece essa coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:27.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só se encontrem no Grove 46 com\Nos cem recrutas que achamos aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele homem de nariz comprido...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquela mulher de cabelo laranja...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele moleque com capa e mochila gigante...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achem aqueles três...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:43.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e façam eles se arrependerem\Nde ter cruzado o Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Oh! Entendido!\N– Oh! Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:48.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos tentar não matá-los\Nantes de trazê-los aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:52.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos usar essa oportunidade\Npra mostrar que não é brincadeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:54.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom, vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esperem um pouco, vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:00.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esses dois anos mudaram tanto\Na personalidade de vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:05.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu... eu... tô tão triste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tudo que eu consigo é chorar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De novo, o que é essa criatura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:14.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E a Robin? Por que vocês\Nnão dizem alguma coisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:16.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Como ele consegue falar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os brinquedos de hoje são bem avançados!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:23.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Vocês não são nada\Ndo que eu pensava que fossem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:27.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou salvar ela sozinho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:34.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me espera, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem alguma briga interna?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:41.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São eles...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sem dúvida nenhuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:48.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Piratas do Chapéu de Palha podem parecer\Nmuito diferentes de dois anos atrás,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:52.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas ninguém mais tem um bichinho estranho desses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,os Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles tão vivos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:05.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui é o Grove 47. Identificamos positivamente\No grupo pirata como os Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:16.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}{\q2}Aparentemente, todos os piratas que o Chapéu de Palha recrutou\Nnessa ilha estão se reunindo no Grove 46!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido! Recebido!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Evacuem os civis imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Recebido!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:27.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Piratas se reunindo no Grove 46!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:31.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O alvo são os Chapéu de Palha!\NVamos invadir a área sem lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se para ação!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:37.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cerquem eles pelos\NGroves 40, 42 e 44!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Reforço do G-1 tá a caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sentomaru, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou liderar o ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:56.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,PX-5 e PX-7 virão comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...? Vai mandar os pacifistas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:06.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos vocês estão subestimando os Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:10.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já faz dois anos desde a guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles com certeza ficaram mais fortes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:17.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles não são como os novatos\Nque normalmente vêm pra essa ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O significado por trás...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:27.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,das ações do Warlord Kuma\Nde dois anos atrás continuam um mistério.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:35.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porém, eu observei como ele se comportou\Ndepois de perder sua personalidade,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:41.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(5100,6500,\3c&HFFFFFF&,\4c&HFFFFFF&)}me levando a concluir que os Chapéu de Palha\Nse reuniriam aqui um dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra onde levaram ela?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:11.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Droga! Droga! Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:15.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com todo mundo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:22.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy, Zoro, Nami, Sanji, Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles costumavam ser tão compassivos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Robin é sequestrada e\Nele diz "deixa pra lá"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É muito cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:38.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra que... pra que eu trabalhei tanto\Nnesses últimos dois anos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E por quem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:47.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia que era o Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:04.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cara, você ficou enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aposto que agora é confortável andar em você!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cê tá bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:09.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aham!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:13.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É verdade! Você tá muito mais macio que antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faz tempo, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:18.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Opa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:22.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:22.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sou eu mesma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:29.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz em ver vocês,\Nmas tá acabando o tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)}A Robin tá em perigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Quer dizer que eles são impostores?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por isso que tem duas Namis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:49.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Robin escapou do governo\Npor vinte anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:53.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É impensável que ela pudesse ser enfiada\Nnum saco e levada tão facilmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:54.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu achei que tinha algo errado...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O cheiro dela nem era familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:03.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, agora eu tô com raiva!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem eles pensam que são, se passando por nós?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:10.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eles ousam nos imitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É quase como se a gente fosse...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,como se... como se...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:19.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,como se a gente fosse os originais, esses patifes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você tá tão feliz?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:26.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, acho que ter imitadores era inevitável,\Ncom a fama do nosso capitão.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:30.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eu vou assinar meu autógrafo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh! Eu já decidi o meu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:36.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês sabem que esse não é\No tipo bom de fama, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:45.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:53.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cara! Demos sorte de achar o verdadeiro\Nbichinho dos Chapéu de Palha, mas já perdemos ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:56.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai! Meu lado!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:58.02,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(475,0)}O que você disse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:02.49,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquela criatura estranha era\Ndos verdadeiros Chapéu de Palha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.83,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que não falou isso antes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.82,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Vá buscar ele de volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.23,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(860,1410,1,\c&HFEFEFE&\3c&HFEFEFE&\4c&HFEFEFE&)}– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:12.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente nunca vai achar ele se\Nnão souber onde procurar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:16.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Perdemos ele completamente!\NO Sabaody Archipelago é grande demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai! Meu lado! Tá doendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:24.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não dá mais pra correr!\NVamos... vamos só andar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:30.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Hancock tinha razão. Preciso desse bigode.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela me disse pra não arranjar confusão.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Olha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:40.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o moleque de capa com mochila\Nque o Capitão mencionou?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você chama isso de moleque?\NParece mais um velhinho animado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Opa? Ei, galera!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:52.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei, mano. Vamos dar uma volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:55.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só vem quieto e não vai ter problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:15:00.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nosso capitão tá muito bravo.\NDesiste de viver muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Tá com medo demais pra falar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:07.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é o Sanji, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.47,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então você é o Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:12.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo, galera!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.38,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-O quê...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:15.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei, faz tempo! Né?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:17.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I-É! Então vamos indo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, já tá todo mundo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa por fazer vocês esperarem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:31.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que ele confundiu a gente?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso nem importa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:35.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos só levar ele pro capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui é o Grove 46.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:58.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cada vez mais novatos estão se juntando\Naos Chapéu de Palha e aparecendo aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:01.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vejo quatro capitães.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.55,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,Com uma recompensa de 92 milhões de belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:06.05,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,Albion, o Mutilado.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.87,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,Com uma recompensa de 88 milhões de belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.79,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,Lip "Service" Doughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:15.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-E... tem uns super novatos...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.27,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,O capitão dos Piratas do Caribou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.63,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,Com uma recompensa de 210 milhões de belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.57,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,"Cabelo Molhado" Caribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.55,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,E o irmão dele e co-capitão.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.98,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,Com uma recompensa de 190 milhões de belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:30.21,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,"Respingo de Sangue" Coribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:43.79,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Bis! Bis! Bis! Bis!\N– Bis! Bis! Bis! Bis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:49.59,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Bis! Bis! Bis!\N– Bis! Bis! Bis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi. Os Marinheiros, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:54.56,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Bis! Bis! Bis!\N– Bis! Bis! Bis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:56.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não empurre!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:58.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Soul King! Volte pra gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:58.74,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Bis! Bis! Bis!\N– Bis! Bis! Bis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preciso de mais um tempinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:04.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim... Meus fãs estão pedindo bis...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:04.71,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Bis! Bis! Bis!\N– Bis! Bis! Bis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:09.98,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Bis! Bis! Bis!\N– Bis! Bis! Bis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:14.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e como eles não param,\Neu tenho que voltar ao palco.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:14.52,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Bis! Bis! Bis!\N– Bis! Bis! Bis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por esperarem, todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:42.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)}{\i1}É isso! O show acabou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Marinheiros estão aqui? Mas por quê...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:50.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão interino dos Piratas Rumbar:\N"Espadachim Cantarolante" Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Recompensa: 33 milhões de belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:56.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Suspeitamos que você é esse mesmo pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Além disso,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:03.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nossa inteligência diz que você atualmente\Nfaz parte da tripulação do Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soul King Brook—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ou melhor, Brook, o pirata—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,você está preso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser... Nosso querido Brook não é...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Soul King é um criminoso?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é um pirata?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:22.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eu ouvi que o Chapéu de Palha Luffy tinha morrido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acabou, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:29.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu achei que você podia estar por trás disso...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Empresário.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:35.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando você me contou nos bastidores\Nsobre seus planos de aposentadoria,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,me deu um choque enorme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:42.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você ficou tão popular que a gente tava\Nprestes a lucrar muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:47.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você nos traiu, e nossa agência\Nvai falir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:54.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos morrer juntos, Soul King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.69,Main-207+,,0,0,5,,Legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:05.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Né?! O corpo dele é incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é como um robô!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:17.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Consegue disparar raios ou mísseis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:19.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Consegue se combinar com alguma coisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Naturalmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Carregando as paixões e sonhos dos homens
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Enquanto entra em ação está ele
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Aquele que eu chamo de,
Comment: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:31.03,Armored Me Main,,0,0,0,,{=104}====ARMORED ME====
